sg":"<blockquote>由iphone4s開始都有呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n上google搵「iphone 個人熱點 斷線」大把人有同樣情況, 唔知點解咁多年都係咁樣</blockquote><br />\n我有d fd都話iPhone 熱點差<br />\n不過佢地話好少用 無咩影響<br />\n但連登仔個個都無呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0107c2ffd1426cbf8c8ee46f5f38d6393b565f4c","tid":400783,"uid":27616,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"你部機有問題，我日日用都冇問題"},{"pid":"364e243152773ee09d146c726f99f485c33fcb41","tid":400783,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由iphone4s開始都有呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n上google搵「iphone 個人熱點 斷線」大把人有同樣情況, 唔知點解咁多年都係咁樣</blockquote><br />\n我有d fd都話iPhone 熱點差<br />\n不過佢地話好少用 無咩影響<br />\n但連登仔個個都無呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出街剩係帶iphone咪無呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n我用開share出黎比ipad間中都會因為有1分鐘左右無用Data令到個功能自己停止<br />\n<br />\n所以今次出iphone 8同X搞到我想買X都只好買番8，我唔想次次斷線都攞過部電話出黎解鎖著番個功能佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea43fb82fcc78ed5ca11cf67e20cc8ab8862c25","tid":400783,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得啖笑"},{"pid":"5409b15d33656e76d334ddf98ae8b655b5a92d21","tid":400783,"uid":1419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"你個嘢壞咗啊"},{"pid":"f3dbd079af75dc1b91d2a1a1fb44dfbb3b9991db","tid":400783,"uid":12034,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"見到條藍色條就唔撚開胃"},{"pid":"713baa649fa11373e200e0959390dbe53f1b0beb","tid":400783,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到條藍色條就唔撚開胃</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nAgree <br />\n弱智到爆，洗唔洗用咁大地方"},{"pid":"fc21183d8c1dbb8842648600c7221baac3e44337","tid":400783,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"我係唐樓無得揀日日都要靠iphone個熱點，但用咗成年只係試過三四次會突然斷咗線，基本上如果無野連緊個熱點就一定要開返熱點果頁先會連到，連緊果陣都要喺返果頁<br />\n<br />\n不過因為我長用，所以次次都係插住電，同埋因為要長連先可以keep住個熱點，可能有啲notebook set咗wifi省電模式，所以個熱點當斷咗線"},{"pid":"75b465e70c321c04415461f82072c60580b46d3d","tid":400783,"uid":4519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"無你地個問題，但個moon唔熄得，個moon一熄隔一陣就會自己斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc20c08901750176756b3d5b9c087077d74d783","tid":400783,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無你地個問題，但個moon唔熄得，個moon一熄隔一陣就會自己斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人經驗你有連左其他野，條藍色bar出現左就唔會斷，之後記住去番設定-&gt;personal hotspot果頁關mon就多數無問題<br />\n<br />\n唔洗特登開住個mon<br />\n<br />\n但網上睇過呢個問題係話本身IOS系統設計成咁<br />\n<br />\n你連左線但隔一陣唔用Data，佢就會自己休眠，通常呢個情況我就咁用TouchID解鎖佢自己去番personal hotspot果頁就會著番，唔算好大問題<br />\n<br />\n但無TouchID我就唔知佢點搞呢個問題啦"},{"pid":"aedbcc8682dfb94605f50bf119a28e63d0ea9c80","tid":400783,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"係咪用98蚊任上plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7501f248fc6706e29ea6326fe3559984bcfcb41","tid":400783,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:12:19.000Z","msg":"128kb ?<br />\n356kb? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a5efc78f9280a304d5050cd332dfa14c69476","tid":400783,"uid":78252,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"每次都要開關兩三次先會連到<br />\n<br />\n試過同幾個fd去旅行，夾錢買sim card插朋友A部iphone黎share wifi，然後開頭唔得，就off and on個hotspot功能，之後得左，就大家一齊用<br />\n<br />\n再之後有時試兩次都唔得，朋友A就嫌煩，阻住佢上網，就唔再試到得為止，自己開心上網，其他人無wifi用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔左好耐之後，我地問可唔可以試多次，佢用發脾氣既口吻話 頭先咪試左囉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3388cdb3a8a802d1b8c93e8883a726d88bf3bae1","tid":400783,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"android 個個真係好好"},{"pid":"dea89405b8bd22dd6e1847f1b0b1a3aaacdc2045","tid":400783,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"熱點真係唔係成日連到"},{"pid":"b888a5636ff1fa7ae754c3a61d0c509820a023f0","tid":400783,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"成日要重開wifi先連到"},{"pid":"d02961cbbe078b5afa91e1bf5e851fb76cab38ec","tid":400783,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"起連登講IP壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7597caff81d7887af6510dd777c3afa92189d8cc","tid":400783,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"iPad 連要開藍芽同wifi, 開少一樣都唔得"},{"pid":"33591e2f2ceb442b18ba8482b0d73815272b38a2","tid":400783,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"我用緊wifi 再開熱點 點先可以唔用個wifi 淨係用熱點"},{"pid":"dd1bdc42fe787e096380f5f1660eca6deb530e9b","tid":400783,"uid":19431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"5s都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0037b551c1efb31de1a9cfbfe588ed6f298c80a","tid":400783,"uid":19431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次都要開關兩三次先會連到<br />\n<br />\n試過同幾個fd去旅行，夾錢買sim card插朋友A部iphone黎share wifi，然後開頭唔得